Asana cli
=========

Done
====
  - Ability to list tasks in a project, run: 'asana list <unique-project-name-fragment>' 
    e.g.  asana list simple site
          asana list site #it lists the first project which matches this name

  - Ability to add tasks to a project, run: 'asana add  <unique-project-name-fragment> This is an awesome task'
    e.g.  asana add 'Simple Site' This is an awesome task
          asana add site This is an awesome task

